{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"margin","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/CSS/margin","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"介绍","title":"介绍","isH3":false,"content":"<p>TTSS 简写属性，控制元素所有四条边的外边距属性。一个元素的外边距控制的是元素外部空出的空间。该属性可以为负值，默认为0。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">/* 应用于所有边 */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* 上边下边 | 左边右边 */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 5% -10%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* 上边 | 左边右边 | 下边 */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> -1em 2em 2em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* 上边 | 右边 | 下边 | 左边 */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 5px -1em 0 2em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"取值","title":"取值","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><code>&lt;length&gt;</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>以固定值为外边距。</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><code>&lt;percentage&gt;</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>相对于包含块的宽度，以百分比值为外边距。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"标准化语法","title":"标准化语法","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">margin: [&lt;length&gt; | &lt;percentage&gt;]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>1<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 4<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例子","title":"例子","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>view</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>outside<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>text</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>此元素会显示在包含块之外。<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>text</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>view</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">.outside</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 3em 0 0 -3em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 66%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"介绍","id":"介绍"},{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"例子","id":"例子"}],"summary":"TTSS 简写属性，控制元素所有四条边的外边距属性。一个元素的外边距控制的是元素外部空出的空间。该属性可以为负值，默认为0。","popularity":0,"modified":null,"other_translations":[{"title":"margin","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/css/margin","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/css/m